        <div rend="parallel">
          <p xml:id="Kali124-kilavi">itu "veḷippaṭa varaital paṭāmai varaitaleṉ ṟāyi raṇ ṭeṉpa varaita lāṟē" (to.po.140) eṉpataṉāṟ kaḷavu veḷippaṭṭapiṉ varaiyātu poruḷvayiṟ pirintu vantāṉait tōḻi etirppaṭṭu niṉṟu talaiviyatu āṟṟāmai kūṟi varaivukaṭāyatu.</p>
          <p xml:lang="en"></p>
        </div>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="Kali124">
                <l>ñālamūṉ ṟaṭittāya mutalvaṟku mutumuṟaip </l>
                <l>pālaṉṉa mēṉiyā ṉaṇipeṟat taiiya </l>
                <l>nīlanī ruṭaipōlat takaipeṟṟa veṇṭirai </l>
                <l>vālekkar vāycūḻum vayaṅkunīrt taṇcērppa;</l>
                <l rend="space">ūrala reṭuttaraṟṟa vuḷḷāynī tuṟattaliṟ </l>
                <l>kūruntaṉ ṉevvanō yeṉṉaiyu maṟaittāṇmaṟ </l>
                <l>kārikai peṟṟataṉ kaviṉvāṭak kaluḻpāṅkē </l>
                <l>pīrala raṇikoṇṭa piṟainuta lallākkāl;</l>
                <l rend="space">iṇaipivvū ralartūṟṟa veyyāynī tuṟattaliṟ </l>
                <l>puṇaiyillā vevvanō yeṉṉaiyu maṟaittāṇmaṟ </l>
                <l>ṟuṇaiyāruṭ ṭakaipeṟṟat toṉṉala miḻantiṉi </l>
                <l>yaṇivaṉap piḻantata ṉaṇaimeṉṟō ḷallākkāl;</l>
                <l rend="space">iṉṟivvū ralartūṟṟa veyyāynī tuṟattali</l>
                <l>ṉiṉṟataṉ ṉevvanō yeṉṉaiyu maṟaittāṇmaṉ </l>
                <l>veṉṟavē ṉutiyēykkum viṟaṉala ṉiḻantiṉi </l>
                <l>niṉṟanī rukakkaluḻu neṭumperuṅka ṇallākkāl;</l>
                <l rend="space">ataṉāṟ,</l>
                <l>pirivillāy pōlanī teyvattiṟ ṟeḷittakkā </l>
                <l>lariteṉṉā ṭuṇintava ḷāynalam peyartarap </l>
                <l>puriyuḷaik kalimāṉṟēr kaṭavupu </l>
                <l>viritaṇṭār viyaṉmārpa viraikaniṉ celavē.</l>
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
                <l>O man from the cool coast of glowing water that surrounds pure dune areas</l>
                <l>white waves that obtained fitness like the dress of blue water</l>
                <l>ornately fixed on him with a body like milk,</l>
                <l corresp="1-4">in sequence older than the first one who stretched out [his] feet for the three worlds.</l>
                <l>You who won’t think of lamenting when the village raises gossip, because of your abandoning [her],</l>
                <l>she hides her troubling pain that is much even from me,</l>
                <l>thus weeping when her beauty fades that a woman gets,</l>
                <l corresp="5-8">if it was not  for [her] forehead that had taken as ornament the sponge-gourd blossom. </l>
                <l>You who don’t know that this villages in unison spreads gossip, because of your abandoning [her],</l>
                <l>she hides [her] troubled pain that is without support even from me,</l>
                <l>as [her] old beauty is lost that obtained precedence among [her] companions, </l>
                <l corresp="9-12">if not for her shoulders soft to touch that have now lost [their] ornate beauty.</l>
                <l>You who don’t know that today this village spreads gossip, because of your abandoning [her],</l>
                <l>she hides her troubling pain that is constant even from me,</l>
                <l>as [her] victorious beauty is lost that resembles the tip of a victorious spear</l>
                <l corresp="13-16">if it were not for [her] long big eyes that weep so that now tears are shed that are constant.</l>
                <l corresp="17">Therefore,</l>
                <l>so that the choice beauty returns of her who is determined, who said “it will be difficult”</l>
                <l>at the time you confirmed before the god as if you would not separate,</l>
                <l>urging on the chariot with spirited horses with plumes in strands.</l>
                <l corresp="18-21">o man with a wide chest with an expanding cool garland, make haste with your going.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
